### ======================================================
### STAGEFLOW - BOOKING ADMIN
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@studioSlug = studio-beat-lab
@adminToken = REPLACE_ADMIN_TOKEN

### ✅ Listar reservas do studio (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/studios/{{studioSlug}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ✅ Listar clientes do studio (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/studios/{{studioSlug}}/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ❌ Sem token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/studios/{{studioSlug}}/bookings

### ❌ Token inválido (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/studios/{{studioSlug}}/clients
Authorization: Bearer token-invalido
